Ancient Wrath

After over 1 year of work i am proud to present you my first Zombie Escape map.
Countless hourse of mapping and an unusual amount of thought went into this project.

Map features:

  • Custom Textures 
  • Custom Music 
  • Custom Particles 
  • Custom Sounds 
  • 5 Human Weapons 
  • 2 Zombie Weapons 
  • 4 Stages

You can download the CSGO version here.


This is the full version of the map no updates till v2!
Please report any bugs in the commands below.
A fixed version will be released with v2.
